    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Tendrils of darkness curl out from your fingertips and race through the air. You deal 2d4 negative damage and 1 persistent bleed damage to living creatures in the line. Each living creature in the line must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The creature is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The creature takes half the negative damage and no persistent bleed damage.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The creature takes full damage.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  The creature takes double negative damage and double persistent bleed damage.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (+1)</b>  The negative damage increases by 2d4, and the persistent bleed damage increases by 1.</p>",
